    <recordLookups>
        <description>This action retrieves some accounts for you to test the component.
It retrieves all accounts that were modified within the last 14 days.
Please be aware that if there are no accounts that were modified within the last 14 days, you won&apos;t see anything. If there are more than a few hundred accounts - the flow might throw an exception. Please try limiting the number of records selected within a reasonable amount.</description>
